                    <p><strong>Dose (per CPP-009-AO, EOC authorised):</strong></p>
                    <div class="dose-highlight">
                        <strong>Patient ≥ 6 years (or ≥ 25 kg): IM Glucagon 1 mg</strong>
                    </div>

                    <h4>Preparation</h4>
                    <ol class="steps">
                        <li>Retrieve Glucagon kit from drug bag</li>
                        <li>Reconstitute: Add diluent (water for injection) to powder vial</li>
                        <li>Gently swirl until dissolved — do not shake vigorously</li>
                        <li>Draw up 1 mg (entire vial) into syringe</li>
                    </ol>

