                    <ol class="steps">
                        <li>Select site: <strong>Lateral thigh</strong> (easiest in seated patient) or deltoid</li>
                        <li>Clean site with alcohol swab</li>
                        <li>Insert needle at 90° angle to skin</li>
                        <li>Aspirate briefly — if blood, withdraw and select new site</li>
                        <li>Inject medication steadily</li>
                        <li>Withdraw needle, apply pressure with gauze</li>
                        <li>Dispose of sharps safely</li>
                        <li>Document time of administration</li>
